    {
      "title": "Running the app",
      "description": "## Running Assistant0 for the first time\n\n1. Select [this link](command:workbench.action.debug.start) to deploy the application. \n\n1. Select the **Open in Browser** in the dialog that appears in the bottom right corner to visit your app's URL. \n>If you miss the dialog, you can always select the PORTS tab below next to TERMINALs and then hover over the FORWARDED ADDRESS and select the globe icon to open your app's URL.\n\n1. Sign up for the application.\n1. Once logged in, try asking it *\"What can you help me with?\"*",
